The Cybersecurity Bootcamp at 4Geeks Academy is a 16-week program designed to help individuals become cybersecurity specialists. With no prior knowledge required, this bootcamp provides a solid foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration.

Participants will learn practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, cyber threat intelligence analysis, and risk management using strategies such as data loss prevention. The bootcamp includes 3 live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 people.

Upon completion, participants will receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by multiple institutions. This bootcamp is suitable for individuals with no previous experience in cybersecurity.

For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. 

